- Baiklah.
- Apa?

714
00:46:14,740 --> 00:46:15,921
Apa?

715
00:46:17,465 --> 00:46:19,547
Bolehkah kita makan bersama?

716
00:46:35,883 --> 00:46:37,390
- Hei.
- Awak sudah makan?

717
00:46:37,415 --> 00:46:38,556
- Baiklah.
